author: David Culver and Ben Westcott, CNN
title: Wuhan is on a slow path back to normality after 76-day coronavirus lockdown
description: The first city in the world to go into lockdown due to the coronavirus is slowly returning to something that might be described as normal, after months of fear and anxiety.
content:
